This is the setup used for:

  Malone, C. M., Zingale, M., Nonaka, A., Almgren, A. S., & Bell,
  J. B., "Multidimensional Modeling of Type I X-ray
  Bursts. II. Two-Dimensional Convection in a Mixed H/He Accretor",
  2014, ApJ, 788, 115

  Zingale, M., Malone, C. M., Nonaka, A., Almgren, A. S., & Bell,
  J. B., 2014, "Comparisons of Two- and Three-Dimensional Convection in
  Type I X-ray Bursts", 2015, ApJ, 807, 60

The relevant inputs files and initial models are in production/current/
